messages.content: Although we'd be launching Gujarat in a month, You can meanwhile discuss with Satish (co-founder) at 7661933372

Sure Mr. Moin,
Thanks for reaching out.

Dear 1Acre.in Team,

I hope this message finds you well. My name is Moin Pariyani, and I am writing to express my interest in your potential expansion into the Gujarat region. I am a real estate professional with extensive experience in land ownership, development, and construction in my hometown of Jasdan, Rajkot, Gujarat.

I believe that there is significant potential for your business in this region, and I would be delighted to discuss how we might collaborate to ensure the success of your expansion.

I look forward to hearing from you.

Best regards,
Moin Pariyani
+91-8347798692
